definition: to sell/to make or carry out (a plan or intrigue etc)

sentences.english: In Mali, women's groups make unsell and sell soap produced with chetrofur jatropha seeds.
sentences.chinese: 在馬裏，女人們一組組地製售用麻風樹種子做的肥皂。

sentences.english: Counterfeiting medicines can be very lucrative.
sentences.chinese: 製售假冒藥品有大利可圖。
